{"tid":671675,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"柏天尼爆98世盃抽籤做馬","createTime":"2018-05-20T10:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T11:47:52.000Z","uid":52978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e5bb2feaab67b7ce74884b49311d06c53a3876","tid":671675,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20180520/20396257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F20396257&d=gvcWd9NFaIJSdc%2B8%2FS%2FdbpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=201fc9d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F20396257&h=e164e113\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20180520/20396257</a><br />\n<br />\n前法國名宿兼前歐洲足協主席柏天尼爆料稱，1998年法國主辦嘅世界盃，法國足總就做咗「小技倆」，以確保東道主唔會喺決賽前夕，即淘汰賽階段碰上當時大熱巴西，以保送法國殺入決賽，最終亦憑住呢個「走線」之利，喺決賽一舉擊敗巴西捧走世盃。<br />\n柏天尼表示，法國同巴西原本係隨機分配到唔同嘅小組，但籌辦世盃嘅法國足總就做咗「手腳」，以確保巴西進入A組，而法國就被安排喺C組，咁樣嘅分配下只要兩支球隊都順利首名出線，就可以肯定唔會喺決賽前相遇。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋唔覺得有咩嘢問題，花咗六年時間嚟籌辦世盃，點可能唔做一啲手腳。」柏天尼繼續踢爆：「你會相信其他主辦國，真係冇做手腳嗎？」的而且確，歷屆咁多支主辦國都喺抽籤上佔到甜頭，其中今屆世盃主辦國俄羅斯，分配喺A組嘅對手亦只係烏拉圭、事隔28年再闖決賽周嘅埃及，同埋32支球隊中世界排名最低嘅沙地阿拉伯，被外界認為係上籤有力爭取出線。"},{"pid":"3ceeb27ef8ebad837086ddf1f9a20064052a1ace","tid":671675,"uid":52978,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"柏天尼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲講到理直氣壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae87f82ad0bab6544129642a689edd01173ac4b3","tid":671675,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"